  "Witherhoard": {perk:"Villainy", desc:"Rounds create a lingering blight pool that deals damage over time, even while you swap weapons."},

  "Borealis": {perk:"Ionic Return", desc:"Breaking a shield matching this weapon's current element refills the magazine from reserves and grants bonus damage for the rest of the mag. A separate perk, The Fundamentals, lets you swap its damage type between Arc, Solar, and Void."},
  "Buried Bloodline": {perk:"Never Missed a Day", desc:"Weakening a target and then killing it activates Devour, healing you on subsequent kills."},
