  "Hard Light": {perk:"Volatile Light", desc:"Rounds have no damage falloff, overpenetrate targets, and ricochet off hard surfaces \u2014 each bounce increases the bullet's damage. A separate perk, The Fundamentals, lets you hold reload to cycle its damage type between Arc, Solar, and Void."},
  "Hawkmoon": {perk:"Paracausal Shot", desc:"A hidden roulette occasionally lines up a guaranteed critical hit; landing it starts a damage-boosting streak."},
